      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, has been maintained to an exacting standard. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this specimen offers an uncompromising driving experience for the most fastidious of owners. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
