    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty\u2014it is in pristine condition and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I have taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream! If you are looking for a ride that feels brand new but without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. I am so excited for the next owner to enjoy it. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 46500.0,
