      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a superlative example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated VANOS system. This vehicle has undergone a comprehensive mechanical audit, including proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a full cooling system overhaul. The 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical accuracy, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis retains its original rigidity, benefiting from refreshed bushings and a flawlessly preserved suspension geometry. Finished in museum-grade paint with a pristine Nappa leather interior, this specimen represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division performance. No deferred maintenance; purely an investment-grade driving machine.",
